text: I've been seeing Dr. Chee for many years, and she is my first pick for a clinic in the Keat Hong neighbourhood since she is very kind and attentive. So far, I have had no issues with the clinic assistants because they are very polite and have never been rude to me or my family.

Doctor is a nice and polite lady, nurses are helpful.

This clinic is associated with Parkway Shenton.

Their op time is a little tough for me to keep track. And during my urgent moments, I tend to be disappointed.
Dr Chee is very kind and meticulous. She is good with kids too. She has been our family doctor for a few years.
Each time i visited her i get cured fast. She also has injection options which heal faster
